		        &copy; {{ page.date.getFullYear() }} Tea and Scones Press. All rights reserved.<br><a class="copyright" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/charmainezoe/50367422056">Tea and scones image</a> &copy; Flickr user <a class="copyright" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/charmainezoe/">CharmaineZoe</a> licensed under <a class="copyright" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/">CC BY 2.0</a>.
		      </div>
		    </div>
